metadata.name: Unlimited
metadata.description:
Turn inwards to sense your own magic. Be bold and brave to discover your own inner light. Find out who you truly are. See that what you are has no limitations. You were always free... From here you can do anything. 

Size: 70x100x4cm

Materials: mixed media (acrylic pouring, golden leaf, inks, oil paint) on gallery wrapped canvas (no framing required)

Year: 2022

Original one-of-a-kind painting by Anna Sun artist

This painting was a breakthrough for me, a taste of my own freedom and breaking free from any limitations. It's a sense of I am here and I claim my space and my own unique path
